		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>
<DIV>The downside for someone like me&nbsp;is that my guild would be separated and split across the servers, since we have a huge range of levels. For that reason, I would never want it to happen. Aside from that, I have to admit it would probably do very good things for the game.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The sort of thing I would rather see, is a series of cross-server zones for certain level ranges, where the ability to trade/drop items doesn't exist. You could just zone in to group with like-level characters from other servers, without having to leave any friends behind.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The chances of either one happening are probably a bit slim, but they're&nbsp;interesting to think about&nbsp;<img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-wink.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0>.</DIV></DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
