<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
MrFsh wrote:<BR>
<DIV>
<DIV>The downside for someone like me&nbsp;is that my guild would be separated and split across the servers, since we have a huge range of levels. </DIV>
<DIV>
<HR>
</DIV></DIV></BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>Not only that, but alts would be spread across servers as well.&nbsp; It's also ripe for abuse.&nbsp; Can you see someone saccing 100 times just so they unding a couple levels, and get poofed to another server, with all their high level gear and stuff.</P>
